"
    }
   },
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "<!-- ![Screenshot 2025-06-23 at 11.43.34.png](attachment:290fc94d-2358-44d9-829c-220cd96a8b34.png) -->\n",
    "<img\n",
